GERTRUDE DUKES et vir, et al., v. FINN BONDHOLDERS, INC. 26 So. (2nd) 805

June'Term, 1946

June 25, 1946 Division B Rehearing denied July 22, 1946 Erie B. Askew, W. K. Zewadski and J. Lewis Hall for petitioners. Carey & Harrison, for respondents. *649PER CURIAM:

Petition certiorari denied. (See opinion in Finn Bondholders, Inc., et al., Appellants, v. Gertrude Dukes, et vir et al., Appellees, filed this day.)

CHAPMAN, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
